import { Box, Icon, Paper, Stack, Typography } from "@material-ui/core";
import {Timeline, TimelineConnector, TimelineContent, TimelineItem, TimelineOppositeContent, TimelineSeparator} from '@material-ui/lab';
import Cart from '../images/trolley.svg';
import Shoppers from "../images/shoppers.png";



function WorkHistory() {
    return (
        <Box alignItems='center' component={Stack} backgroundColor='re'>
            <Timeline position='alternate'>
                <TimelineItem>
                    <TimelineOppositeContent
                      sx={{ m: 'auto 0' }}
                      align="right">
                          <Typography>2015 - Present</Typography>
                    </TimelineOppositeContent>
                    <TimelineSeparator>
                        <Icon component='img' src={Cart} sx={{fontSize:'4rem'}}/>
                        <TimelineConnector />
                    </TimelineSeparator>
                    <TimelineContent>
                        <Paper elevation='2' sx={{py:1, px:3 , borderRadius:'0.5rem'}}>
                            <Stack spacing={2} width='18rem' direction='row' justifyContent='space-between'>
                                <Icon component='img' src={Shoppers} sx={{fontSize:'5rem'}} />
                                <Box>
                                    <Typography textAlign='center' fontSize='1.2rem' fontWeight='500'>Shoppers Food - UNFI</Typography>
                                    <Typography textAlign='center'>Deli Clerk</Typography>
                                    <Typography textAlign='center'>Laurel, MD</Typography>
                                </Box>
                            </Stack>
                        </Paper>
                    </TimelineContent>
                </TimelineItem>
            </Timeline>
        </Box>
    )
}


export default WorkHistory;
